description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you passionate about patient care?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic registered mental health nurses to join our staff bank, to work as required within our acute hospital setting.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are currently recruiting dedicated and motivated individuals across a variety of disciplines to join the Staff Bank at North Devon District Hospital based in Barnstaple.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do you want?:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• To be an integral member of a dedicated team working within your local hospital?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• To join a forward thinking and innovative organisation, which puts their patients first?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• To contribute to the provision of high quality care within your local community?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you do, then we want to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can offer flexible working and attractive salary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are currently employed by the Trust and want to join the Northern Healthcare Trust Staff Bank then please contact the recruitment team at ndht.staffbank@nhs.net as you do not need to apply for this vacancy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interviews will be completed via Skype, Zoom or telephone during the current pandemic climate.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
